translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,98,Chunacha koi basti eman na laee kay eman lana uss ko nafey hota siwaye younus (alh-e-salam) ki qom kay. Jab woh eman ley aaye to hum ney ruswaee kay azab ko dunyawi zindagi mein unn per say taal diya aur unn ko aik waqt (khas) tak kay liye zindagi say faeeda uthaney (ka moqa) diya
  10,99,Aur agar aap ka rab chahata to tamam roy-e-zamin kay log sab kay sab eman latay to kiya aap logon per zabardasti ker saktay hain yahan tak kay woh momin hi ho jayen
  10,100,Halankay kissi shaks ka eman lana Allah kay hukum kay baghair mumkin nahi. Aur Allah Taalaa bey aqal logon per gandagi daal deta hai
  10,101,Aap keh dijiye kay tum ghor kero kay kiya kiya cheezen aasmanon mein aur zamin mein hain aur jo log eman nahi latay unn ko nishaniyan aur dhamkiyan kuch faeeda nahi phonchatin
  10,102,So woh log sirf unn logon kay say waqiyaat ka intizar ker rahey hain jo inn say pehlay guzr chukay hain. Aap farma dijiye kay acha to tum intizar mein raho mein bhi tumharay sath intizar kerney walon mein hun
  10,103,Phir hum apney payghumbaron ko aur eman walon ko bacha letay thay issi tarah humaray zimmay hai kay hum eman walon ko nijat diya kertay hain
  10,104,Aap keh dijiye kay aey logo! Tum meray deen ki taraf say shak mein ho to mein inn maboodon ki ibadat nahi kerta jin ki tum Allah ko chor ker ibadat kertay ho lekin haan uss Allah ki ibadat kerta hun jo tumhari jaan qabz kerta hai. Aur mujh ko yeh hukum hua hai kay mein eman laney walon mein say hun
  10,105,Aur yeh kay apna rukh yaksoo hoker (iss) deen ki taraf ker lena aur kabhi mushrikon mein say na hona
  10,106,Aur Allah ko chor ker aisi cheez ki ibadat mat kerna jo tujh ko na koi nafa phoncha sakay aur na koi zarrar phoncha sakay. Phir agar aisa kiya to tum iss halat mein zalimon mein say ho jao gay